WEBVTT

00:08:59.800 --> 00:09:04.320
but the very worst legacy
that we can leave our children is lies.

00:09:04.760 --> 00:09:09.976
We can no longer afford
to shield the kids from the ugly truth

00:09:10.000 --> 00:09:13.920
because we need their imagination
to invent the solutions.

00:09:14.720 --> 00:09:19.696
So citizen scientists, makers, dreamers --

00:09:19.720 --> 00:09:22.416
we must prepare the next generation

00:09:22.440 --> 00:09:25.496
that cares about
the environment and people,

00:09:25.520 --> 00:09:27.720
and that can actually
do something about it.

00:09:28.200 --> 00:09:29.416
Thank you.

00:09:29.440 --> 00:09:32.600
(Applause)